attributes.Long form description: The teacher gives the task of disassembling the knaverrick side bed table,so the student starts by unscrewing the first leg from the table top using the allen wrench.Then the student unscrews the second leg from the table top with the allen wrench and so with the third and fourth leg of the table.Then manually the student removes all the screws from the table top so he can remove the table top. The student continues by disassembling the first leg from the shelf using the allen wrench and so unscrewing the screws of the second, third and fourth legs until the student removes the rest of the screws manually of the shelf.The student removes the shelf and finally the  student stacks all parts, the shelf, the legs and the table top together. And the student finishes the task.

attributes.Transcription: We will now disassemble the bedside table from IKEA. So please go ahead.

attributes.Action sentence: The student unscrews the screws from the table top using an Allen wrench.

attributes.Incorrect Action Explanation: the screw isn't supposed to fall to the floor.

attributes.Action sentence: The student removes the table top.
The student disassembles the first leg from the shelf.
The student disassembles the second leg from the shelf.

attributes.Incorrect Action Explanation: The furniture isn't supposed to fall.

attributes.Action sentence: The student disassembles the third leg from the shelf.

attributes.Action Correctness: Wrong Action, corrected by instructor verbally
attributes.Incorrect Action Explanation: The student should flip it into the side.

attributes.Transcription: You can flip it into the side.

attributes.Action sentence: The student disassembles the fourth leg from the shelf.
